### Tests manuels du module Utilisateurs (token ADMIN requis)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

### Login admin
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "admin@transport.ma", "password": "Passw0rd!" }

@token = {{login.response.body.accessToken}}

### Lister (pagination + recherche + filtre statut)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?page=1&limit=10&search=&sortBy=id&sortOrder=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Créer
# @name create
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nom": "Nadia Fassi",
  "email": "nadia@transport.ma",
  "telephone": "+212600000099",
  "motDePasse": "Passw0rd!",
  "idRole": 2,
  "statut": "ACTIF"
}

### Créer avec e-mail existant -> 409
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "nom": "Doublon", "email": "nadia@transport.ma", "motDePasse": "Passw0rd!", "idRole": 2 }

### Créer avec rôle inexistant -> 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "nom": "X", "email": "x@transport.ma", "motDePasse": "Passw0rd!", "idRole": 9999 }

### Détail
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{create.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Modifier (sans changer le mot de passe)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/{{create.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "telephone": "+212611111111", "statut": "SUSPENDU" }

### Supprimer
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/{{create.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
